.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-install 1  "install 0.1.1" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-install \- Install a pack from the registry
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp install\fR [\fB\-g\fR|\fB\-\-global\fR] [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-dest\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-registry\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-\-token\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-verify\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fINAME\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Install a pack from the registry
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-g\fR, \fB\-\-global\fR
Install to global store (~/.dkp/packs/)
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-dest\fR \fI<DIR>\fR
Install to a custom directory
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-registry\fR \fI<URL>\fR
Override registry URL
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-\-token\fR \fI<KEY>\fR
Registry API token
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-verify\fR
Skip signature verification (NOT RECOMMENDED)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fINAME\fR>
Pack name, e.g. @mathis/nutrition\-for\-men or @mathis/pack@1.2.0
.SH VERSION
v0.1.1
